OL,6,FClifford McKeown died last week ` just
OL,7,Fmonths after being released from
OL,8,Fprison. He was the longest serving
OL,9,Fparamilitary prisoner in Northern
OL,10,FIreland.
OL,12,FHe was convicted of Mr McGoldrick's
OL,13,Fmurder while already in prison serving
OL,14,Fa sentence for possessing firearms.
OL,16,FWidow Sadie told UTV she was numb when
OL,17,Fshe heard the news.
