OL,6,FAsked if McKeown's death has given her
OL,7,Fclosure, she replied: ''No, I don't
OL,8,Fthink you ever get closure. It is
OL,9,Fsomething that is going to be with me
OL,10,Ffor the rest of my life."
OL,12,FMcKeown's brother Trevor was convicted
OL,13,Fof the murder of 18-year-old
OL,14,FBernadette Martin in Aghalee in July
OL,15,F1997.
OL,17,FThe gun used to shot the teenager in
OL,18,Fher boyfriend's home ` the same one
OL,19,Fused to kill Mr McGoldrick.
